          'We are providing high-quality stationery, including notebooks, pens, art supplies and more to support students in their everyday learning.',
        icon: 'tabler:ruler',
      },
      
      
      {
        title: 'Consultancy',
        description:
          'Expert guidance for schools on management, technology integration and operational efficiency.',
        icon: 'tabler:messages',
