    title="Who We Are"
    subtitle="At Unifinity, we are committed to transforming the education sector by providing comprehensive solutions for schools. Our expertise spans across technology, resources and consultancy, ensuring that educational institutions run smoothly and efficiently. We understand the challenges schools face in managing day-to-day operations and we aim to bridge the gap with innovative, reliable and high-quality services. From streamlining administrative processes to enhancing student experiences, we help schools focus on what truly matters—education. With a team of professionals dedicated to excellence, Unifinity is your trusted partner in building a smarter, more efficient and future-ready educational environment."
  />

  <!--Who We Are********* -->


  <!-- Our Vision & Mission Section -->
  <div class="mt-2 space-y-2"> <!-- Reduced vertical space further -->
    <Mission
      id="mission"
      title="Our Mission"
      subtitle=""
      tagline=""
      classes={{ container: 'max-w-6xl' }}
      items={[
        
        {
          description:
            "Our mission is to empower educational institutions with cutting-edge ERP solutions, high-quality books and essential learning resources while also providing premium school uniforms and fashion apparel. We are committed to leveraging innovation, technology and a customer-first approach to enhance efficiency, accessibility and sustainability in both education and lifestyle. By integrating smart digital tools, we aim to simplify school management, improve student learning experiences and foster seamless communication between educators, students and parents. Our curated selection of books and educational materials ensures academic excellence, while our uniforms and apparel uphold quality, comfort and style. With a strong focus on sustainability, we strive to create eco-friendly solutions that reduce waste and promote ethical practices. Through continuous improvement and a passion for excellence, we aspire to be a trusted partner in shaping the future of education and fashion.",
        },
      ]}
    />

    <Mission
      id="vision"
      title="Our Vision"
      subtitle=""
      tagline=""
      classes={{ container: 'max-w-6xl' }}
      items={[
        {
