    {
      // title: 'Why Unifinity',
      description:
        "At Unifinity, we understand the challenges schools face in managing daily operations while striving for academic excellence. That’s why we provide comprehensive, technology-driven solutions designed to streamline school management and enhance the learning experience. Here’s why schools trust us:\n\n" +
        "• One-Stop Solution – From ERP systems, website development, uniforms, stationery and books to consultancy services, we offer everything a school needs under one roof.\n\n" +
        "• Customized & Scalable Solutions – We understand that every institution is unique. Our solutions are tailored to meet your school’s specific needs and scale as your institution grows.\n\n" +
        "• Cutting-Edge Technology – Our advanced ERP systems and digital platforms help schools automate administrative tasks, improve communication and enhance efficiency.\n\n" +
        "• Quality & Reliability – Whether it’s school uniforms, books or stationery, we ensure premium quality materials that meet the highest standards.\n\n" +
        "• Expert Guidance & Support – Our experienced team provides end-to-end consultancy to help schools implement the best solutions for seamless operations and student success.\n\n" +
        "• Cost-Effective & Time-Saving – We help schools reduce operational costs and save valuable time by integrating smart, efficient solutions that simplify management.\n\n" +
        "Partner with us and experience a smarter, more efficient way to manage your school.\n\n" +
